snippet.title: Ascendum Final Devlog - 4,5 Years of Struggle
snippet.description:
After more than 4 years, Ascendum is finally done, for sure this time.
Ascendum on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1504090/Ascendum/

Team Caecus Discord:
https://discord.gg/GtZar6DZr4

Play Ruins of Albion on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1719100/Ruins_of_Albion/

Wishlist Virium on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1923230/Virium/

Caecus on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TCaecus
Tumblr: https://teamcaecus.tumblr.com/

Follow the composer Lukian:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lukianze/
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/user-864799849-361065325
